These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  writer, manager, nurse, architect, dressmaker, freelancer, photographer
House: palace, cape-cod, art-deco, colonial, modern, ranch-style, wooden
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: climbing, golf, parkour, surfing, tennis, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the cape-cod house and the palace house##2
 4. the architect is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the manager##1
 6. the writer is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the colonial house is between the person who's sport is surfing and the dressmaker##2
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the photographer is the art-deco house##1
11. the ranch-style house is the architect##1
12. the photographer is on the left of the nurse##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is the modern house##1
14. the freelancer is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Job   | dressmaker | writer     | freelancer | manager | architect | photographer  | nurse  |
| House   | palace  | colonial        | cape-cod  | wooden     | ranch-style   | art-deco       | modern   |
| Sport         | golf   | water-polo | surfing    | parkour  | tennis | volleyball | climbing |

