.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, chess, whist, snooker, canasta, domino, bridge
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, almond-milk, tea, fanta, coffee, cola
 1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is the person playing chess##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Game   | domino | bridge      | snooker     | backgammon  | canasta | whist | chess |
| Sport         | cricket  | badminton | snowboarding | handball | soccer | parkour   | sailing  |
| Beverage     | almond-milk   | coffee     | cola        | tea  | fanta   | mirinda       | iced-tea      |

