 5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 9. the fan of pop is the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the fan of electronic is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person driving the car is the fan of reggae##1
12. the person eating banana is the fan of country##1
13. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the car and the person driving the bus##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person driving the train##1

