 1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsazalea##2
 3. the person who growslily is the person who likes amber##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person who growslily is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the person who growslily is the person who likes amber##1
10. the writer is the person who likes lilac##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
14. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

