 2. the person driving the trike is the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person drinking coffee is the person eating pepper##1
13. the person driving the ship is the person eating blueberry##1
14. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the boat##1
15. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

